title: Ninja Zan
description:
This is a real photo, not a photoshop composite!
Strobist info: Start with Zan in flight. He looks fierce, lands, and cowers from his alter ego, all while spinning Flowtoys light staves. 2-second exposure with both front and rear curtain flash, radio-triggering Sunpak 622s in umbrellas camera left and right and one in the background camera left for rim lighting.
